name: Investing in Startups & Identifying the Rocketship Summit
description: Google, Silicon Valley Bank, and Salesforce-sponsored summit moderated by Forbes VC Senior Editor, Alex Conrad, and founded by Aku Aakriti Srikanth. Summit brings together leading investors like General Catalyst Managing Partner, Quentin Clark, and corporate executives like CTO of Microsoft, Lila Tretikov to network and talk about investing and building startups.
